🌷 Another Stories Intimates Admin

A feminine, poetic approach to retail management —
because even closing numbers can tell a beautiful story.

🩰 Overview

Another Stories Intimates Admin is a concept admin system inspired by the lingerie brand Love Stories.
It’s designed for boutique staff and managers who value beauty, warmth, and emotional connection — even in everyday tasks like reporting sales or managing shifts.

This project reimagines the admin dashboard as a soft, human workspace — elegant, intuitive, and emotionally engaging.

✨ Concept

Unlike typical admin tools that feel mechanical or cold,
this interface invites users to pause, reflect, and record their “daily story.”
It blends functional clarity with a sense of intimacy,
transforming daily management into a personal ritual.

🕊️ Because behind every number, there’s a story.

🧩 Features
🏢 HQ (Headquarters)

Overview dashboard (sales, staff activity, events)

Employee database (employment type, wage, contact info, notes)

Store performance summaries

Editable event calendar

Inter-store chat and internal blog view

🏬 Store Branch

Daily report input (sales, returns, notes)

Local dashboard with charts

Shift scheduling and editing

Chat and blog access

Calendar editing for store events

👩‍💼 Individual Staff

Personal shift view

Profile editing (photo, contact, role)

Internal chat and blog access

Calendar sync with store schedule

🎨 Design Direction

A gentle mix of professional minimalism and soft femininity.
The design draws inspiration from lingerie textures — subtle, intimate, yet structured.

Element	Style
Color Palette	Soft Ivory #FFF8F4, Dusty Rose #EBD4CF, Terracotta #D98C6A, Mauve Taupe #B58B8B, Sage #B6C4AA
Typography	Playfair Display (titles) × Inter (UI)
UI Tone	Rounded corners, airy spacing, calm gradients, and subtle animations
Microcopy	“Beautifully saved — your story is complete.” 🌷
🛠️ Tech Stack

React + TypeScript

Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Storage)

Tailwind CSS

Framer Motion for soft animations

Recharts for data visualization

🌿 UX Keywords

softness · transparency · self-expression · rhythm · care

💬 Future Plans

Push notifications for staff chat

Analytics dashboard for HQ

Shift auto-generation system


